        "zh": "1.\t創業動機與構想<br>2.\t產品與服務內容<br>3.\t市場與競爭分析<br>4.\t行銷策略<br>5.\t財務規劃與風險分析<br>6.\t結論與投資效益<br>",
        "en": "1. Entrepreneurship motivations and ideas<br>2. Product and service content<br>3. Market and competition analysis<br>4. Marketing Strategy<br>5. Financial planning and risk analysis<br>6. Conclusion and investment benefits<br>"
